milestones.description: Jekon Edness and Chris Douglas's 90-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 80 between Dean Minors and Romaine
Karun Jethi and Baidwan's 72-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 31 between John Davison and Umar Bhatti
Canada's 26-run win against Bermuda is the smallest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 56-run win against Bermuda
